                            Soy usuario nuevo
                        </h1>

                        <div class="m--padding-10">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center m--padding-5" style="margin:auto;display:flex;border-radius: 60px;background-color:white;border:1px solid #0f7f97">
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" style="padding:unset;">
                                    <a asp-action="Register" asp-controller="Account" style="" class="btn m-btn--pill btn-secondary btn-block">BUSCO ABOGADO</a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" style="padding:unset;">
                                    <a href="#" style="" class="btn m-btn--pill btn-lc-green btn-block text-white">SOY ABOGADO</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
